Gerda, why don't you go?

935
01:29:44,255 --> 01:29:46,279
- He asked me not to.
- He wanted to protect you.

936
01:29:46,379 --> 01:29:50,229
- You should be there. I'll go with you.
- If I go, it will be alone.

937
01:29:52,737 --> 01:29:56,173
- Now you're sounding like Einar.
- I am like Einar.

938
01:29:59,371 --> 01:30:02,306
- What do you want me to do?
- I want you to go away.

939
01:30:03,350 --> 01:30:04,250
Really?

940
01:30:12,199 --> 01:30:13,856
No... I... sorry...

