955
01:32:50,747 --> 01:32:52,197
You made me beautiful,

956
01:32:54,597 --> 01:32:56,447
Now you're making me strong.

957
01:33:00,710 --> 01:33:02,510
Such a power in you.

958
01:33:09,560 --> 01:33:11,510
Shall we go back to Denmark then, Gerda?

959
