1038
01:39:37,424 --> 01:39:38,724
Just tell him...

1039
01:39:40,929 --> 01:39:44,129
Tell him it's a beautiful day
in Copenhagen

1040
01:39:48,673 --> 01:39:50,573
- Good morning.
