thinks that I am.

1052
01:40:47,213 --> 01:40:50,147
Warnekros? Warnekros
hasn't seen you. 

1053
01:40:50,247 --> 01:40:51,697
I've made up my mind, Gerda.

1054
01:40:52,845 --> 01:40:56,145
- It could kill you.
